_Sparsh_ [comments](http://yayaver.blogspot.com/2010/01/jihad-against-caste-
discrimination.html) on the still persisting caste discrimination in India: “I
always ask elders that society has become more feudal, caste oriented and
communal than 60 years ago. No clear cut answers. People still ask with smile
surname to map out the caste and ancestry in their minds.”

